                            <comment id="14319829" author="ay" created="Fri, 13 Feb 2015 10:25:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am not sure if this is reproducible. I just tried with one of the existing cxf samples and didn&apos;t see this problem.&lt;br/&gt;
