                            <comment id="14381996" author="ay" created="Thu, 26 Mar 2015 14:57:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Carlos,&lt;br/&gt;
indeed. As you have described, there seems to be a problem when the endpoint address is not assigned from elsewhere (e.g. via wsdl) and the binding is fetched prior to publishing the endpoint.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i&apos;ll push the fix shortly.&lt;br/&gt;
thanks.&lt;br/&gt;
regards, aki&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
